Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Hi, this is John from TerraVista Properties. Am I speaking with Mary?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, this is Mary.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Hi Mary! I appreciate you taking the time to chat today. How are you doing?

Speaker: Customer
Text: I'm doing well, thank you. How about you?

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I'm great, thank you. I see you've been looking at some properties on our website. Is there a specific type of home you're interested in?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, I'm looking for a three-bedroom home, preferably with a decent backyard. We have two kids, so space is important.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: That makes sense. Is there a particular area you're looking at?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Ideally in the Lakeside neighborhood because the schools there are really good, but I've seen that prices are pretty high.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Lakeside is a wonderful area, and I understand the concern about pricing. Have you set a budget for your new home?

Speaker: Customer
Text: We’re looking to stay under $500,000 if possible, but everything in Lakeside seems to be above that.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: I can see how that would be frustrating. One thing we can do is look at homes that might need a little updating. They can sometimes be priced more affordably.

Speaker: Customer
Text: Hmm, I hadn't considered that. But isn't that risky? I don't want to end up with huge renovation costs.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: That's a valid concern. At TerraVista, we have trusted inspectors and contractors who can give you a realistic estimate of what any necessary work might cost, so you can make an informed decision.

Speaker: Customer
Text: That does help a bit. I just want to make sure we're making a good investment.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Absolutely, and we're here to help with that. How soon are you looking to move?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Ideally within the next three to six months.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Great, that gives us some time to find the right place for you. I’ll start by sending you some listings that match your criteria but might be slightly outside the Lakeside area or in need of minor updates. Does that sound good?

Speaker: Customer
Text: Yes, that sounds like a good plan.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Perfect, I’ll get those over to you by tomorrow. If you have any questions or if there's anything specific you want to see, just let me know.

Speaker: Customer
Text: Will do. Thanks for your help, John.

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: My pleasure, Mary. Looking forward to finding the perfect home for you and your family. Have a great day!

Speaker: Customer
Text: You too, bye!

Speaker: Sales Rep
Text: Bye!
